\c 57
\p
\v 1 Wakarurama anoparara, zvino hakuna munhu anozviisa pamoyo; uye vanhu vane tsitsi vanobviswa, pasina anorangarira kuti wakarurama anobviswa kubva pane zvakaipa.
\v 2 Achapinda \add mu\add*rugare, vachazorora pamibhedha yavo, umwe neumwe achifamba \add pa\add*uchokwadi hwake.
\p
\v 3 Asi swederai pano, imwi vanakomana vemukadzi muroyi, chibereko chemhombwe, nemukadzi chifeve.
\v 4 Munotambira ani? Munoshamisira ani muromo, muchibudisa rurimi? Hamusi vana vekudarika, chibereko chenhema here?
\v 5 Munozvipfutidza pakati pemiouki, pasi pemuti umwe neumwe mutema, muchiuraya vana mumipata, pasi pemikaha yemabwe.
\v 6 Mugove wako uri pakati pe\add mabwe\add* anotedza erwizi, iwo, iwo achava mujenya wako, uye kwaari wakadurura chipo chechinwiwa, wakapa nechipo chechidyiwa. Ndichazvidemba pane izvi here?
\v 7 Pamusoro pegomo rakareba uye rakakwirira wakaisa nhovo yako, wakakwirawo ipapo kubaira chibairo.
\v 8 Zvino shure kwegonhi nemagwatidziro makaisa chirangaridzo chenyu; nokuti maka\add zvi\add*ratidza \add kune umwe\add* kupfuura ini, uye makakwira; makakurisa mubhedha wenyu, mukazviitira \add sungano\add* navo; wakada mubhedha wavo pawaka\add mu\add*ona.
\v 9 Zvino wakaenda kuna mambo nemafuta, uye wakawanza zvinonhuhwira zvako, ndokutuma nhume dzako kure, zvino uka\add zvi\add*dururira mugehena.
\v 10 Wakaneta muukuru hwenzira yako, \add asi\add* hauna kuti: Hakuna tariro. Wakawana upenyu hweruoko rwako; naizvozvo hauna kupera simba.
\v 11 Zvino wakatya ani ukavhunduswa, kuti utaure nhema usingandirangariri, usina ku\add zvi\add*isa mumoyo mako? Handina kunyarara here, zvirokwazvo kwenguva refu, asi hauna kunditya?
\v 12 Ini ndichaparidza kururama kwako, nemabasa ako, kuti hazvingakubatsiri.
\p
\v 13 Kana uchichema, zvaunga zvako ngazvikununure, asi mhepo ichavapeperesa vose, kushaya maturo kucha\add va\add*tora; asi anovimba neni, nyika ichava yake, achagara nhaka yegomo rangu dzvene.
\v 14 Zvino achati: Tutirai, tutirai, gadzirai nzira, bvisa chigumbuso panzira yevanhu vangu.
\v 15 Nokuti anoreva seizvi ari pamusoro neakakwirira, anogara \add mu\add*kusingaperi, ane zita rinonzi Mutsvene: Ndinogara \add pa\add*kakwirira ne\add pa\add*tsvene, uye pamwe naye ane mweya wakapwanyika uye wakazvininipisa, kuvandudza mweya wevakazvininipisa, nekuvandudza moyo wevakapwanyika.
\v 16 Nokuti handingapikisi nekusingaperi, uye handingatsamwi nguva dzose; nokuti mweya ungapera simba pamberi pangu, nemweya ini yandakaita.
\v 17 Nekuda kwekuipa kwekuchiva kwake ndakatsamwa, ndikamurova, ndikazvivanza, ndakatsamwa, asi wakaenderera achitsauka nenzira yemoyo wake.
\v 18 Ndaona nzira dzake, uye ndichamuporesa, ndichamutungamirirawo, nekudzosa nyaradzo kwaari nekuvachemi vake.
\v 19 Ndinosika chibereko chemiromo; rugare, rugare kune ari kure nekune ari pedo, anoreva Jehovha, zvino ndichamuporesa.
\v 20 Asi vakaipa vakaita segungwa rakabvongodzwa; nokuti harigoni kuzorora, uye mvura yaro zhinji inobudisa matope nemarara.
\v 21 Hakuna rugare, anoreva Mwari wangu, kune vakaipa.